additionalProperty.value: Place a capsule into dispenser drawer and close immediately. Handle with dry hands only. Do not unwrap or puncture the capsule. Reseal the bag after each use.1 capsule = 1 loadFor best results use the dispenser drawer. If the pouch will not fit in the drawer place on top of the cutlery basket and select a washing program with no pre-wash. The Salt Action is effective in soft, medium and hard water up to 26e ( 95% of households). Your dishwasher should work effectively even if the rinse aid or salt warning light comes on.
